 Erick Erickson Show &#8211; Supply Chains</a></h2><div class="article-excerpt"><p>You should really subscribe to my Substack channel. The Erick Erickson Show is live! Here&#8217;s the plan for today: Hour 1 Georgia audit by county Sonny Perdue WGXA in Macon Experts and curation Mic &hellip;</p></div><div class="author-meta post-meta"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/erick-erickson/" class="avatar"><img src="https://theresurgent.com/wp-content/uploads/erick-20-100x100.jpg" alt="Erick Erickson" class="avatar"></a> <span>by <a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/erick-erickson/">Erick Erickson</a></span></div><div class="post-meta time-meta"><time datetime="2020-04-16">3 days ago</time></div></div></div><div class="article-entry d-flex d-md-block"><div class="article-img"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/2020/04/16/michigan-governor-whitmer-is-a-lot-of-backlash-for-her-extreme-stay-at-home-order/"><img width="1400" height="875" src="https://theresurgent.com/wp-content/uploads/iStock-1206091436-1400x875.jpg" class="auto-size" alt="" /></a><div class="author-meta offset-meta"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/joseph-sacco/" class="avatar"><img alt='' src="//theresurgent.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82683e74097300d2398a70ab49abd78d?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset="" data-srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82683e74097300d2398a70ab49abd78d?s=192&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='lazy lazy-hidden avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' /><noscript><img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82683e74097300d2398a70ab49abd78d?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82683e74097300d2398a70ab49abd78d?s=192&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' /></noscript></a> <span>by <a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/joseph-sacco/">Joseph Sacco</a></span></div></div><div clas